ygData.subject: RE: [eqbards] Looking for place to hunt
ygData.msgSnippet: Reaver Hill in E Karana.  I hunted there quite a bit around 20th.  If you see a gnoll named Splintered Claw though, run for the zone immediately. He s a necro
ygData.messageBody:
Reaver Hill in E Karana. I hunted there quite a bit around 20th. If you
see a gnoll named Splintered Claw though, run for the zone immediately.
He's a necro around 24th level and we all know how balanced necro's are.

Kit

Subject: [eqbards] Looking for place to hunt

of day I tend to hunt threre aren't too many people online so
grouping usually isn't an option. Any ideas on where I can solo?

PS I am posting this to several groups so my apologies if you see
this more than once.

Shaman of 18 seasons
